    <h3 class="help-heading">How to use this website</h3>

    <p class="help-par"><span class="help-highlight">Objective:</span> Create tailored playlits based on your desired features. Based on a myriad of audio features 
        that you select and fine tunes, the spotify algorhythm will provide recommended tracks.
    </p>

    <!-- <h4 class="help-highlight">Instructions</h4> -->
    <p class="help-par" >
        <span class="help-highlight">Instructions:</span> For each feature in the required section(artist, track and genre), select at least one of each, with a maximun
        of 5 per field. 
    </p>
    <p class="help-par">
        You can further fine tune your search result by using audio features. To activate an audio feature, click the
        tick mark next to the feature. The item will no longer be grayed out and the value will be taken into account. 
        Just use the slider to set the desired level. 
    </p>
    <p class="help-par">
        If you want to explore acoustic songs, you want to ramp up the acoustic values, easy. There 
        is also an option to add more features than the default through the advanced features option. 
    </p>
    <p class="help-par">
        Then search. The recommended songs will be displayed. If you want to add these
        to a playlist, select the add to playlist option. You can then either create a new playlist or add the songs
        to an existing playlist. 
    </p>
